To enroll in Full Service Direct Deposit, simply fill out this form and give it to your Human Resource Generalist. Attach a voided
check for each checking account – not a deposit slip. If depositing into a savings account, ask your bank to give you the
Routing/Transit Number for your account. It isn’t always the same as the number on the savings deposit slip. This will help ensure
that you are paid correctly.
Below is a sample check MICR line detailing where the information necessary to complete this form can be found.




